oring and unhappy little man ever since his ex-wife left him two years ago. To make matters worse, his 16-year-old son has started avoiding him. Things change when Pignon's psychologist neighbor persuades him that he can save his job by coming out to his employers as a gay man -- even though he isn't.   GREETINGS: Welcome back  Tubs ! 
     
    
